Note on derived work: this Julia port re-implements the algorithms from
Devon Powell's r3d library (https://github.com/devonmpowell/r3d), which
was developed at Los Alamos National Laboratory under contract
DE-AC52-06NA25396 and released for free public use under a notice
preservation requirement. The original r3d notice is preserved in the
relevant source files (R3D.jl/src/clip.jl, moments.jl) where the algorithm
attribution is given to Powell & Abel (2015), J. Comput. Phys. 297:340-356.
